invalid type: string "Credit Reference Agencies (CRA) upon applying for a loan? \nIn normal circumstances, PBHK will request a credit report of applicant from \nthe CRA to collect  the information about his/her credit history and \nindebtedness. Applicant who wants to acquire the credit report, please \ncontact PBHK and the bank will provide the contact detail of relevant CRA. \nication. \n \nĸĸĸĸ